{"tid":562864,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"學生哥望增高識女神","createTime":"2018-02-16T10:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T10:19:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"332dbe93c9ef6bb67b11bb0d7c8273273b93668f","tid":562864,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180216/20307163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F20307163&d=6R1NWmwuYKdQhY7l7wlf8TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=765f10fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F20307163&h=6df7eae2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180216/20307163</a><br />\n<br />\n學生哥望增高識女神<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n狗年來臨，學生哥各有不同願望，小一的梁同學最實際，希望「成績好啲，可以買多啲玩具」；小二的袁同學則希望不要再遲交功課，有患濕疹同學仔希望來年濕疹受控，並在學校校慶表演跳繩時順利；小二的劉同學希望獲得1,000元大利是，可以購買iPhone和iPad，更渴望不用做家務。<br />\n<br />\n至於中一的鄭同學則希望可以增高，「最好有1.6米」；他的波友李同學（圖）除希望籃球技術提升，亦夢想結識一名長髮可愛女朋友；中二的何同學希望選修合適科目，並可獲派公屋「上樓」改善居住環境；他的同學王同學則希望可去海洋公園玩。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃麗兒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180216/large/16la5p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F16la5p11.jpg&h=21815d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t動記者去求籤　問香港狗年運程<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t或有高官下台　法治存暗湧<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t林鄭治港跟習主席？港人：依家嘅政府無希望<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t股市大上大落　樓價仍高企<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t攝太歲後需擇吉還神<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t哈日情侶想中六合彩<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t《蘋果》求籤　港運勢入秋有轉機一國兩制續受威脅　雙鄭民望恐插水<br />\n要聞 11小時前"},{"pid":"1d4a47c21d549e0d265f8bad99fdebdc821fbbb9","tid":562864,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/175915_904376dee0ebc7b5ffd05a702b69ffbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F175915_904376dee0ebc7b5ffd05a702b69ffbe.png&h=1229f69e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食菜可高，試過，利申183大隻m男。"},{"pid":"47c424d20e774b3d6d979781354a03723bd52372","tid":562864,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"眼鏡男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n王心凌新玩具"},{"pid":"9547e34fb3c42c16f50b2d4c07c709895eb3cb73","tid":562864,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:19:07.000Z","msg":"全部都係操蝗語嘅蝗"}]}